      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and will require significant mechanical and cosmetic work to be fully functional. The exterior shows heavy wear, including noticeable rust patches, peeling clear coat, and several large dents across the body panels. Inside, the cabin has seen better days, with torn upholstery, cracked dashboard plastic, and non-functional electronics. Mechanically, the engine starts but runs roughly, and there are persistent leaks and suspension noises that need immediate professional attention. This car is sold strictly as-is and is best suited for someone looking for a major restoration project or a source for parts.",
