      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hi there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and she\u2019s looking for a new home! Honestly, this car has been so reliable and still looks great on the road. It's been well-loved and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for your daily commute or weekend adventures. I've kept up with the maintenance, so it's ready for you to jump in and go. Come take it for a spin, you're going to love how it handles!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
